    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a bit of a weird way to put it lol. i'm not looking for a story, i need to understand the actual mechanics for a technical exam. can you explain exactly how the two materials interact at a structural level during a loading event? like, what happens to the stress distribution when the concrete starts to experience tension?",
